{"type":"message","id":"b8049c68","parentId":"424c1dd9","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:38:04.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Inspecting cron status**\n\nI think I should inspect the cron status and check the watchdog job logs. Since it's a watchdog cron job, it might be necessary to perform a health check as well. I need to determine if it's functioning properly, perhaps by checking the gateway status or using session_status. A simple step could be to check if the openclaw gateway is accessible by executing a command like curl on localhost. I should also take a look at the /tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log for more insights.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0eab17b1f069f3e80169c2afd6592481919d8a940b05fc648f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwq_aTeQcESb0ALY_xfbIliKPRDCXc7Hu3bY2DJDe5oT8n1i1ECAFBn6NG36pfUUdTsQ3cVjVNxGL7848Ak2Fn3YvJvIgp8e7mbS-mfujkAHxKNfzT_L3Gwg6zEEDFLqpL-ZiizUfDuNQZGaj1AmBPsulLzF7ywdMhR6zDon4FLI_SnMu4sP0Jn1k4Wk828MKtpets52DdArgcNUxDd_R2__bOZdeBHxXyMYvj9WVwNUlX5qSL1h2ZBbF1Nr1thY1YrcnACmtDZfAZVOP25fpKazCfIgIwzGPr1s3hkZaWPKFri2bavB1-CsrStyOVTEX1QIQs0fv8xeWMMX-5aWK1LyO7FDvjuFSaLoiLacVJwnh1qBqDaxkp28yly9siVqKZtBn73fEq1INQAYjhT7eBZj_QPU3nv-bDqDXbn6dbi0H4Lj-PiJoqA7wkE70bfTwlq9aAHbP8FtAKyrnZ1T2mmfj2rZJbbbq_qbSsYZ7eafFUE29OF-4QNRnB3lvBc-Q7W3hWwsDLw14i-5vkV0WI5BQcmYmJK5Xstop-XFeCt52Qc2BCmtCw7Xk1pFGI6ueZKigv7WVMX7aqNUDuTUo2ErR_LIHlBJFFt_CfkRk3aTNXYKk5DYlaLLCELOi8gGga0TRfiQ-a3fyYpjD1Uc1_Dx-Xsr5ZayxjmsRaSuENdApqIrKXqgLZTNqcsxvTWiSHTQk-nhLHmQl3dtxgdqqFvqlBtwK2BS0ViSHq1OnkjpHaBFJ-BvgU2t5kXvLaWXsa66Gm7DDbh_dYwoBx_GhtaWLVpjlxtdwMKMVgcCncy-Uco8dK8gamnUuwDqhBXAfQ8gaERryPZeqDEfZ-L2aPg83aZeE6QuHB9r_LpBn4ocymtr8aCs5-qU05WyK3DD3SAVRfKDWoj0S48SNsf4ayyDSp5QYwfzAO5gdEztzC93EojOHaYOZyx4c1ILaOKdJETsOBEyv5bNx1C6ZH8OvEpuOjBUaEfI-LFVidyrfUTL-BZuYlPAvD2pl2gSACCjaeNBMLsglLY1uC0fflQykU3gSTK80GR6ZtH4R_n-9jLGbowGJQqdYQOOi75DiKOXe2feowuOho7hsY6H-gkQ_6F8_oUHuphb7sH5gkKLQ0Pe396XZBBgRPBp0pJpdkmh1nC9Roe7hYBrp_UXwNwUWg95KEWb2q0EW0vC