{"type":"message","id":"536dc5a8","parentId":"3a072864","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:38:15.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Assessing gateway status**\n\nI think I need to check the gateway status live. It looks like the gateway is currently healthy, which is great! But I noticed that the watchdog log seems truncated or incomplete after the restart. I wonder if I should mention that no immediate action is needed, but it might be a good idea to verify everything looks good during the next run. Just keeping an eye on it to make sure all is well!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0eab17b1f069f3e80169c2afe17aa08191a13ae12d58cb24cb\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwq_m3qSguhGvz9KR9zXzpJ0Wvyd1YBXD5xtA1MYs36DDrfOJtBBFOyBViYJl0SlLeqpNjTbMSB1ZUSt8AlHRuUXm3kektRZezMHZiUJtHaUhwmHxJsgRlaf3KEu3QHg72WjRh0IOE_5AZ0sWAIOmZWaydFIjrDdqASTXuxM-th2WMoIc9Z1DAAg2gozYj2_Il-SxzwrloRmuUFuNRDC7KjjzjX6U5WsUM9WNtutotplmDEf9hIjgBHqxwpdXdwESLEVxdtyIRooHP0lPqsa3pQvvxYRehvkIQjRLBD7cr0h7JonbjlIvw6mHyp3iASh6dMmEDOaYE3Hd6AFQW-ZmVk-7GOJcSd6QpvWtgGw1WLerLByUE-UQ6QvB2Rz3tX1S4b1MOJ81yKFXxWxSJuHUYSVNMXESugscgbBIZI8szYiuER1B_pFKIM7CRgaB2PU3u9MubSsMjO7yuggojDX5DhiCIc0dPnxAFe4i6QqlSMf9Qv51hUIEZXsA1iZzsatx6PLipxpMSaGWKnbi9Nw-V1AKW5IkmEJP3fDr167QEE2OkWMWbPvfdGGD8qOUxdPfs5BiNnUNKASPpXGQ_GlydTXpMkxuYeRbj_jcLQRYVI85REwuztPcZ8BENC9Lrwl6zy4YES72IG8Y6MAe1Ui11e80TB3sB5K4clQJTR9Koc2MLrk0bQ-wFyyGsRfXQ9CMpbC9HD6qWpkBR4cNWkr9ZOFCvK9QeEVOWKhaGHiyBt3RVHuK-RisGEJcrYrBb7DnpICvPUJoqm-h1G67bV8_K5WJPrlW20HHScM1AKhavh-9CDkmwYYFrD942T5K8wcbahbeByBV0xNfGpzRWm5lPY-Tb8wk__mbTu4pBVg2FfSguGud7xTMR9atZot2NPUZApOucvxl1ukfEL_UCJNV4lsQ5JKYBqadbz7ItdBCIbdLf_YTPJ7UK3_DBOZV90rKMAw3BdYiw0mkgrH_TpNklSDGg4P1mUCyyYGB38ZbBtXrwq8mtOsJbTThGRfowlARLN7bsTPyMOyokA1fzI0oA4hoD2smY34ihypsme_Rya7fpdc=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Assessing gateway status**\\n\\nI think I need to check the gateway status live. It looks like the gateway is currently healthy, which is great! But I noticed that the watchdog log seems truncated or incomplete after the restart. I wonder if I should mention that no immediate action is needed, but it might be a good idea to verify everything looks good during the next run. Just keeping an eye on it to make sure all is well!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Watchdog 检查摘要：\n\n- 当前网关可达：`http://127.0.0.1:18789/health` 返回 `{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}`\n- 进程侧未看到明显“OpenClaw 主进程名”特征，但健康接口正常，说明服务当前是活的\n- `/tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log` 最近一次记录显示：\n  - `23:18:22` 首次探测失败\n  - 等待 30 秒后再次失败\n  - `23:18:53` 开始执行 restart\n- 但日志尾部停在 `executing restart...`，没有看到这次重启后的补完结果，像是：\n  - 日志写入在重启过程中中断，或\n  - 重启后续成功但没把结尾刷进日志\n\n结论：\n- **当前状态：服务已恢复/可用**\n- **异常事实：23:18 左右确实发生过一次两连失败并触发自动重启**\n- **待观察点：watchdog 日志补完性不够，建议下次把“restart 后复检结果/最终结论”也强制落日志，方便追溯**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0eab17b1f069f3e80169c2afe6e6388191902e5462b50a5a8a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":303,"output":312,"cacheRead":16384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16999,"cost":{"input":0.0007575,"output":0.00468,"cacheRead":0.004096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0095335}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774366688138,"responseId":"resp_0eab17b1f069f3e80169c2afe088248191b22a178d50a13ac9"}}
